Package com.example.myapplication

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AboutUsActivity
    This is the AboutUsActivity responsible for the representation of the user
    BT
    This is the BT(Bluetooth) Activity in charge of connecting to the already paired devices to send the user input to send commands to the robot.It is also in charge of uploading data to the server according to the commands of the user.
    CheckSensorsActivity
    This is a public class called CheckSensorsActivity
    ExampleInstrumentedTest
    Instrumented test, which will execute on an Android device.
    ExampleUnitTest
    Example local unit test, which will execute on the development machine (host).
    MainActivity
    This is the MainActivity which is responsible for the splash screen
    MenuActivity
    The MenuActivity is the main screen after the splash screen to navigate through the app according to the wants of the user
    ParametersActivity
    The parametersActivity is in charge of handling the automatic and the manual brightness mode of the user's device
    SensorsAdapter
    The public class SensorsAdapter provides a reusable ArrayAdapter that can be used to display lists of Sensor objects in a ListView or Spinner.
    SensorsAdapter.ViewHolder  
    Utils
    This is the public class Utils
